### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = church-uuid-here
@branchId = branch-uuid-here
@projectId = project-uuid-here
@memberId = member-uuid-here

### Create a new project
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Sanctuary Construction",
  "description": "Building a larger hall for the congregation",
  "targetAmount": 500000.0,
  "branchId": "{{branchId}}",
  "startDate": "2026-05-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### List projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects

### List projects of a branch
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/projects

### Create project item
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects/{{projectId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Roofing",
  "description": "Modern roofing for the sanctuary",
  "targetAmount": 50000.0
}

### List project items
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects/{{projectId}}/items

### List project members
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members

### Add a member to a project
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": "{{memberId}}"
}

### Remove a member from a project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members/{{memberId}}

### Get project progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/projects/{{projectId}}/progress
